column2: She’s a pathological LIAR, CHEATER, and PSYCHO. Lock her up!!
column34:
Too many of us have watched and witnessed through the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard civil court case the proof of Amber Heard‘s lying under oath.

While we watch, more proof emerges, proof that is inadmissible in this civil court case due to “other voices” being recorded. But, we do not accept that she not be held accountable as she continues to lie under oath, degrading our court systems. If she is not held accountable, then our system is a joke and this becomes social injustice!

Too many victims have been left to defend themselves while their abusers get to walk away, unscathed by the harm they’ve inflicted on others. Regardless the countless hours of therapy or time spent healing physical injuries, this is damage that can never truly be undone or forgotten, only ever managed.

We who desire to protect the victims of DV as well as uphold our court systems purity of justice, demand that Amber Heard be charged with perjury and tried in criminal court.

I can’t do it alone, but together we can. PLEASE HELP AND SIGN THE PETITION! ❤️

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

 Please sign the petition and forward it on!

column34:

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

Too many of us have watched and witnessed through the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard civil court case the proof of Amber Heard‘s lying under oath.

While we watch, more proof emerges, proof that is inadmissible in this civil court case due to “other voices” being recorded. But, we do not accept that she not be held accountable as she continues to lie under oath, degrading our court systems. If she is not held accountable, then our system is a joke and this becomes social injustice!

Too many victims have been left to defend themselves while their abusers get to walk away, unscathed by the harm they’ve inflicted on others. Regardless the countless hours of therapy or time spent healing physical injuries, this is damage that can never truly be undone or forgotten, only ever managed.

We who desire to protect the victims of DV as well as uphold our court systems purity of justice, demand that Amber Heard be charged with perjury and tried in criminal court.

I can’t do it alone, but together we can. PLEASE HELP AND SIGN THE PETITION! ❤️

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

 Please sign the petition and forward it on!

Too many of us have watched and witnessed through the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard civil court case the proof of Amber Heard‘s lying under oath.

While we watch, more proof emerges, proof that is inadmissible in this civil court case due to “other voices” being recorded. I can’t do it alone, but together we can. PLEASE HELP AND SIGN THE PETITION! ❤️

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

 Please sign the petition and forward it on!

She swore under oath that her testimony given was the truth, that was the first of numerous lies. If the law wants  the public to trust and believe that lying under oarh is considered perjury, then the same law needs to uphold this and charge Miss Heard for perjury.
column34:
Too many of us have watched and witnessed through the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard civil court case the proof of Amber Heard‘s lying under oath.

While we watch, more proof emerges, proof that is inadmissible in this civil court case due to “other voices” being recorded. But, we do not accept that she not be held accountable as she continues to lie under oath, degrading our court systems. If she is not held accountable, then our system is a joke and this becomes social injustice!

Too many victims have been left to defend themselves while their abusers get to walk away, unscathed by the harm they’ve inflicted on others. Regardless the countless hours of therapy or time spent healing physical injuries, this is damage that can never truly be undone or forgotten, only ever managed.

We who desire to protect the victims of DV as well as uphold our court systems purity of justice, demand that Amber Heard be charged with perjury and tried in criminal court.

I can’t do it alone, but together we can. PLEASE HELP AND SIGN THE PETITION! ❤️

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

 Please sign the petition and forward it on!

Too many of us have watched and witnessed through the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard civil court case the proof of Amber Heard‘s lying under oath.

While we watch, more proof emerges, proof that is inadmissible in this civil court case due to “other voices” being recorded. But, we do not accept that she not be held accountable as she continues to lie under oath, degrading our court systems. If she is not held accountable, then our system is a joke and this becomes social injustice!

Too many victims have been left to defend themselves while their abusers get to walk away, unscathed by the harm they’ve inflicted on others. Regardless the countless hours of therapy or time spent healing physical injuries, this is damage that can never truly be undone or forgotten, only ever managed.

We who desire to protect the victims of DV as well as uphold our court systems purity of justice, demand that Amber Heard be charged with perjury and tried in criminal court.

I can’t do it alone, but together we can. PLEASE HELP AND SIGN THE PETITION! ❤️

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

 Please sign the petition and forward it on!

While we watch, more proof emerges, proof that is inadmissible in this civil court case due to “other voices” being recorded. But, we do not accept that she not be held accountable as she continues to lie under oath, degrading our court systems. If she is not held accountable, then our system is a joke and this becomes social injustice!

Too many victims have been left to defend themselves while their abusers get to walk away, unscathed by the harm they’ve inflicted on others. Regardless the countless hours of therapy or time spent healing physical injuries, this is damage that can never truly be undone or forgotten, only ever managed.

We who desire to protect the victims of DV as well as uphold our court systems purity of justice, demand that Amber Heard be charged with perjury and tried in criminal court.

I can’t do it alone, but together we can. PLEASE HELP AND SIGN THE PETITION! ❤️

Let us tell the world we will not stand for domestic violence or abuse of any kind!

Thank you all for your time and consideration. I genuinely appreciate it.

 Please sign the petition and forward it on!

column2:
Dear President or all staff members, 

I am proud that our shared commitment to slowing  and  stopping COVID-19 has saved lives across Canada & US. We have all made important sacrifices to keep our families, friends and communities safe; and we must stay focused on keeping the curve flat.

But it's time for the government to present a plan to safely and responsibly allow Canadians to travel.

Mr. President, I am worried that Canada & US is standing still while other safe countries start to reopening.

The government must act alongside safe countries in Europe that are now responsibly reopening shops, restaurants, travel and tourism, and build a made in United States and Canada plan that:

Rapidly establishes a national framework to ease interprovincial travel restrictions.

Clearly communicates to Canadians that they can travel safely by air to visit their favorite Canadian tourist destinations.

Establishes reciprocal border agreements with safe countries like those in Europe who have responsibly restarted travel.

Reopening Maryland and rebuilding america economy and build back better plan. 

With many Canadians I need to count on you and my elected officials to recognize my concerns, the need for a responsible plan to safely restart travel as soon as possible.

Road to reopening your small businesses and economy recovery, Reopen all indoor & outdoor dining, slowly getting things back to normal.

Sincerely,

Mr. Keshav Gupta
